<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Hollow Saint</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#0a0a0a;
    color:white;
}

header{
    position:fixed;
    width:100%;
    top:0;
    left:0;
    background:rgba(0,0,0,.8);
    backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    padding:20px 10%;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    z-index:1000;
}

.logo{
    font-size:28px;
    font-weight:900;
    letter-spacing:3px;
}

nav a{
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    margin-left:25px;
    transition:.3s;
}

nav a:hover{
    color:silver;
}

.hero{
    height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    text-align:center;
    background:
    linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.6),rgba(0,0,0,.8)),
    url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1493225457124-a3eb161ffa5f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80');
    background-size:cover;
    background-position:center;
}

.hero h1{
    font-size:90px;
    letter-spacing:8px;
}

.hero p{
    margin-top:15px;
    font-size:20px;
    color:#cfcfcf;
}

.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:30px;
    padding:15px 35px;
    border:2px solid white;
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    transition:.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
    background:white;
    color:black;
}

section{
    padding:100px 10%;
}

.section-title{
    font-size:45px;
    margin-bottom:30px;
    font-weight:900;
}

.about{
    max-width:900px;
    margin:auto;
    text-align:center;
    line-height:1.8;
}

.music-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));
    gap:25px;
}

.card{
    background:#151515;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:15px;
}

.card h3{
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.socials{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    gap:20px;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.socials a{
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    border:1px solid #444;
    padding:12px 25px;
    border-radius:30px;
}

footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:40px;
    border-top:1px solid #222;
    color:#777;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<div class="logo">HOLLOW SAINT</div>

<nav>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#music">Music</a>
<a href="#socials">Socials</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
<div>
<h1>HOLLOW SAINT</h1>
<p>Built From Scars. Driven By Purpose.</p>
<a href="#music" class="btn">Listen Now</a>
</div>
</section>

<section id="about">
<h2 class="section-title">About</h2>

<div class="about">
<p>
Hollow Saint is a Canadian hip-hop artist blending raw storytelling,
ambition, pain, and growth into every track. The name represents
the balance between struggle and purpose—the hollow spaces life
creates and the strength needed to rise above them.
</p>
</div>
</section>

<section id="music">
<h2 class="section-title">Music</h2>

<div class="music-grid">

<div class="card">
<h3>BIG BANDS</h3>
<p>Latest release. A statement record about ambition, sacrifice, and success.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Upcoming Project</h3>
<p>New music arriving soon.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Live Performances</h3>
<p>Booking opportunities and future shows coming soon.</p>
</div>

</div>
</section>

<section id="socials">
<h2 class="section-title">Follow</h2>

<div class="socials">
<a href="#">Instagram</a>
<a href="#">TikTok</a>
<a href="#">Spotify</a>
<a href="#">YouTube</a>
<a href="#">X</a>
</div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
<h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>

<p>Email: booking@hollowsaint.com</p>
<p>Management & Business Inquiries</p>

</section>

<footer>
© 2026 Hollow Saint. All Rights Reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>